    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and would make a practical choice for someone looking for a functional daily driver at an affordable price. The engine and transmission are operational, though you can expect the typical wear and tear associated with a car of this age, including some cosmetic blemishes on the exterior and noticeable thinning of the upholstery inside. While it has been maintained well enough to stay on the road, it may require some minor repairs or parts replacements in the near future to keep it running optimally. It\u2019s a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the frills of a newer model.",
      "price": 21500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 46
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine and transmission are functional, but you should expect some minor oil seeps and a suspension that is starting to feel its mileage. The exterior has some visible wear and tear, including minor dings and fading, and the interior is clean but shows signs of regular use. It's a solid choice for someone looking for a budget-friendly, dependable car that may need a little TLC down the road.",
      "price": 16000.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
